{"type": "article", "id": 50039, "title": "LV 要开球鞋快闪店，以及，高级版的H&M Studio新系列还不错 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2018-02-08T03:56:53Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 32759, "name": "Happy Socks"}, {"id": 37319, "name": "H&M Studio"}, {"id": 188, "name": "LV"}, {"id": 1653, "name": "Michael Kors"}, {"id": 3120, "name": "Levi's"}, {"id": 47654, "name": "Marks&Spencer"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 33, "image": "img/article/article_show/20180208115028AU9hsaMVJ8p5C1gv.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Michael-Kors-sales-shine-as-brand-refresh-efforts-pay-off,945072.html#.WnvC_5P1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Michael Kors 假日季销售强劲，提升全年业绩展望</strong></a> | 截止至 12 月 31 日的三个月内，Michael Kors 集团销售同比增长 6.5%，至 14.4 亿美元。同店销售额下降 3.2%，好于分析师预期的下降 6.8%。其中，Michael Kors 品牌的总收入下降了 2%，去年收购的 Jimmy Choo 贡献了 1.147 亿美元。截至周三开盘前，Michael Kors 集团股票大涨了 7%，全年收入预期提高至 46.6 亿美元。</p><p><a href=\"http://uk.fashionnetwork.com/news/Marks-Spencer-taps-into-data-with-new-partnership,944968.html#.WnvGVZP1UzU\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Marks&amp;Spencer 雇佣数据公司，帮助了解消费者需求</strong></a> | 第三季度，英国零售商 Marks&amp;Spencer 的家居服饰部门业绩下滑 2.3%，拖累整体销售。为了扭转颓势，Marks&amp;Spencer 与 Starcount 合作，将利用其创新的技术解决方案，制定客户需求，预测未来的购买行为。这也是 Marks&amp;Spencer 五年转型计划的一部分，它最近宣布计划重新定位其家居服饰部门，并调整营销团队。</p><p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/business-news/financial/levi-strauss-gets-international-boost-in-1202539881/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>Levi’s 去年销售大涨 7.7%</strong></a> | 截止至 11 月 26 日的 12 个月内，Levi's 集团销售额同比上涨 7.7%，至 49 亿美元。得益于假日季旺盛的消费需求，集团第四季度的销售额上涨了 12.9%，净利润大涨 20.8%，至 1.16 亿美元。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>日本老牌生活方式品牌中川政七商店，新设立了一个“以茶论美”的品牌“<a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-08/salon-nara/\" rel=\"nofollow\">茶论</a>”。4 月 24 日，将在奈良开设第一家门店。 </p><p>茶论的品牌总监是木村宗慎，店内共设有学习茶道的“稽古”、品茶的“喫茶”，以及贩售自有品牌茶具的“见世”三个空间，首家店将开在奈良的“游中川”品牌本店内，创意总监是 good design company 的水野学。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114237OmSieAIJC9LDowsG.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114238sbf7GShR8qJx52wg.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114239kQWOtiDld7ySZjhe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114239qERAva2lJnhTdIxX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.334848\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114239dnW9CEK6kacflXhP.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114240O0g1SWGtiXw4EHQl.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114240RKm3ieGwJNSxa7d6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114241x6FZzdUyTfV5AIe2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114241RtVdbAmGM4Wi0ly3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114242qzyBgCYIQKcioP6n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.668182\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>H&amp;M 旗下最高级的产品线 H&amp;M Studio 将于 2 月 28 日在巴黎时装周发布 2018 春夏系列新品，这一季新品的关键词是“日本”，发布之后就可以直接购买。先来看看提前曝光的几组<a href=\"https://www.fashion-press.net/news/36836\" rel=\"nofollow\"> lookbook</a>： </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114326HtCcjk7OS0e692oq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114326ZHvwiN41TDeBhQKr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114326SV6yDJNlaKYnOik7.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114326fW4yC2t3eJaQid7A.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114327lbPHfR2CXA8kV9ip.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802081143280XW5irfAMGwvod3E.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114328T3Pxjqe1AuCOFl5V.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114328SnULRvyzlOtXhaEf.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018020811432880PcIqO6vdf97rjW.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114328KRZw4Ebg1vst53SU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114329JkiYsxIZCR431dca.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114329hBnDNVG5AsgHuY4S.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201802081143296J4MTHEvdWD0ySmk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114329qvJhFraLKNECYPGe.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114331k3Ie0Y5iw1cVLrOF.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/2018020811433136xRjPTu9OnX0lqy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.highsnobiety.com/p/happy-socks-ss18/#slide-7\" rel=\"nofollow\">Happy Socks </a>庆祝十周年，出了一个纪念版套装。套盒内共有来自品牌不同类别的十双精选的袜子，每双代表品牌历史上的一年。<br></p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114412HFfNYLi3xQAKsbm6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114413PLb8gSmU9BMxh6Ft.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114414OyMqoLS2zW3YTG4X.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114416VovPpFMWOK76142R.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114416ufnDJTh35Srp7HVy.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114416DZdlvVIup2CTkLKO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114417h2GgS1fnlbOUvxe4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114418n7U49ehPNbfd1aAq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114418fvg6nUlmBzJha35G.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114419fbwEQcXk1uK4lS2i.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114427JHR2kwlc03hL4Q7B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114428XWwm2VApJq3ShlLj.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://www.fashionsnap.com/article/2018-02-08/tommyhilfiger-f1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tommy Hilfiger 和 F1 车队梅赛德斯 AMG 签订了合约</a>，从今年开始，作为特别合作伙伴为 AMG 车队的 1500 多名队员提供队服和配饰，也会展开一系列的时尚与赛车结合的 campaign 计划。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114507gCJWfTrLhy4dm89O.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114507bqeNAa25KxZL3Bzn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114513txAFjrdTyhNMeiOn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>去年一年，丑丑的老爸鞋成了潮流，奢侈品牌也不例外。 </p><p>2 月 23 日，<a href=\"http://wwd.com/fashion-news/fashion-scoops/louis-vuitton-opens-sneaker-pop-up-in-new-york-11139670/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LV 将在纽约 Greene 街 122 号开设运动鞋快闪店</a>，持续至 3 月 10 日。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20180208114537WKAn0V5FsJtUvr8d.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.648438\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><br></p><p>题图来自：Happy Socks</p>"}